.\" Man page for format program
.\" Cuervo & Oge - Spring 2015

.TH format 1 "17 March 2015" "CSCI 241" "Oberlin College"

.SH NAME
.B format
\- a program to format your files!

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ./format
[ optional formatting flags ]

.SH DESCRIPTION
This program formats from standard input, can be redirected to a file to write a formated version.

.SH OPTIONS
.IP "-w <some number>"
Changes the line
.B w
idth of the output to
.I "<some number>".
.IP
.I Note:
must be between
.B 1
and
.B 1000
\f\..

.IP "-r"
.B R
ight align the output.

.IP "-j"
.B J
ustify align the output.

.IP "-s"
.B S
kip empty paragraphs.

.IP "-h or -?"
Brings up the
.B h
elp note and returns with a non-zero exit value.

.SH AUTHORS
Andres Cuervo and Alexandre Oge (Spring 2015)

.SH BUGS
    None!
